<!doctype html>
<html class="foreign-affairs" lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="icon" href="../assets/favicons/ministry-of-foreign-affairs.svg" />

    <title>Ministry of Foreign Affairs</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <section class="content">
      <div class="ministry-of-foreign-affairs logo-frame">
        <div class="ministry-of-foreign-affairs logo-lottie">
          <!-- logo animation goes here -->
        </div>
      </div>
      <section class="hero">
        <h1 class="hero-title">We handle matters beyond the Kingdom.</h1>
        <p class="hero-text">
          The Ministry of Foreign Affairs manages diplomatic relationships with external entities
          and works with the Central Ministry on diplomatic missions around the world.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section class="ministers">
        <h2 class="ministers heading">Minister</h2>
        <div class="section-divider"></div>
        <div class="ministers list">
          <div class="minister">
            <div class="minister picture" id="paddington"></div>
            <div class="minister info-box">
              <h4 class="minister name">Paddington</h4>
              <h5 class="minister job-title">Foreign Affairs Minister</h5>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="tasks">
        <h2 class="tasks heading">What we do</h2>
        <div class="section-divider"></div>
        <h3 class="tasks title">Keep the peace</h3>
        <p class="tasks text">
          We maintain healthy and stable relationships with foreign entities to ensure the Kingdom's
          sovereignty and security is not compromised by outside threats.
        </p>
        <h3 class="tasks title">Visit new places</h3>
        <p class="tasks text">
          We assist the Prime Minister with trips to various places around the world, spreading our
          signature friendliness to those that we meet.
        </p>
        <h3 class="tasks title">Give travel advice</h3>
        <p class="tasks text">
          Whether its a new tourist hotspot or travel alert, we'll keep you informed on the latest
          happenings outside of the Kingdom in the
          <a class="link" href="/news/">Government news page</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </section>
    <a class="return" href="/">Return to homepage</a>
  </body>
</html>
